rows.label: qev012102_MSG0001
rows.name: Waugh?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0002
rows.name: Ah! You came for me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0003
rows.name:
You're the best, Chief! I wanna hug you
so hard right now![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0004
rows.name: But...aaaAAAUGH! Ouch...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0005
rows.name: Sorry. I think the fall bruised my...everything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0006
rows.name:
When that thing first had me in its mouth,
I sorta freaked out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0007
rows.name:
But after a minute, this calm came over me,
and I saw its eye right there.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0008
rows.name:
And I thought, "Hey, maybe if I poke that,
it'll let go of me."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0009
rows.name:
I mean, even the buffest gym bro can't work out
his eyeballs, right? They're all equally squishy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0010
rows.name:
Being able to think clearly in a pinch like that is
preeeeetty impressive, if I do say so myself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0011
rows.name:
Where was I? ...Oh, right. The stabby bit. So anyway,
I took my dagger, aimed at the eyeball, and ker-STAB![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0012
rows.name: Heh. Man, it did NOT enjoy that![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0013
rows.name: Thing squawked bloody murder and dropped me![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0014
rows.name: ...Course, then I fell from the sky like a ton of bricks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0015
rows.name:
Guess my awesome plan didn't factor in what would
happen if I was dropped from such a height...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0016
rows.name:
I'll just have to file the whole "crippling fall" part
away under "room for improvement."[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0017
rows.name:
Next time, though! Always learning from past
mistakes, that's me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0018
rows.name: So, um...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0019
rows.name:
Think you could keep up this trend of saving my
buns by lending me a shoulder?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0020
rows.name: I don't think I'll be standing on my own anytime soon...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev012102_MSG0021
rows.name: Ow. Sorry. ...And thanks.[ST:wait ]
